ersion": "shield", "text": "It sucks in dust from the air at an astounding rate, frantically building up energy within its core as preparation for evolution."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "Motionless as if dead, its body is faintly warm to the touch. In the distant past, it was called the cocoon of the stars."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "The absorption of starlight fuels this Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s growth. The shell that encases it is harder than any known material."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "As it absorbs light, Cosmoem continues to grow. Its golden shell is surprisingly solid."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "The king who ruled Alola in times of antiquity called it the \u201ccocoon of the stars\u201d and built an altar to worship it."}], "entryGameVersions": ["moon", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun"], "moveGameGroups": ["scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "cosmog"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "cosmoem"}, {"stage": 3, "name": "lunala"}, {"stage": 3, "name": "solgaleo"}]}